@startuml C4_Register_Shipping_Agents_Logical_View
title C4 – Port Logistics Management System (PLMS) – Logical Deployment View (Shipping Agents)
left to right direction

skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor LightGray
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor Wheat
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam artifact {
  BackgroundColor HoneyDew
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

actor "Organization Representative" as Rep
actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer

node "User Device\n(Laptop / Browser)" as Client {
  artifact "Frontend Web App\n(React / Angular)" as Frontend
}

node "Application Server\n(Docker Container / IIS)" as AppServer {
  artifact "Shipping Agents Management API\n(ASP.NET Core Web API)" as API
}

node "Database Server\n(SQL / SQLite)" as DBServer {
  database "PLMS Database" as Database
}

cloud "External IAM Provider\n(SSO / OAuth 2.0 / OIDC)" as IAM
cloud "Email/SMS Providers\n(SMTP / REST API)" as Notif

Rep --> Frontend : Register organization (HTTPS)
Officer --> Frontend : Review / validate (HTTPS)
Frontend --> IAM : User login (OIDC PKCE)
Frontend --> API : REST (JSON/HTTPS, JWT bearer)
API --> Database : CRUD via EF Core (SQL)
API --> Notif : Confirmation Email/SMS
@enduml
